name: Feathered tales - archetales
description:
Part of Feathered Tales within the Hybrid Mythology universe. Analog piece created using watercolor, markers, ink and acrylics. 

Birds and archetypes of birds feature heavily in lots of my work and with time I have built quite a collection of bird archetypes in different media and mixture of them. Sometimes bird motif would sneak itself into my work, even when I am creating something quite different. I have huge fascination with birds as they posses the super power of flying. There is a tremendous sense of freedom associated with the ability to fly  and there is a great playfulness expressed by bird spirits as well as a sense of mystical.
